@page "/privacy"
@page "/privacy-notice"

<SeoHead Title="Privacy Notice" CanonicalPath="/privacy" NoIndex="true" />
<HeadContent>
    <meta name="description" content="SNL Engineering website privacy notice — how we collect, use, and protect your personal information." />
</HeadContent>

<div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Website Privacy Notice</h1>
        <p>How we handle your personal information on this website</p>
    </div>
</div>

<section class="section">
    <div class="container content-page legal-content">
        <p><em>Last updated: @DateTime.Now.ToString("MMMM yyyy")</em></p>

        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>
            SNL Engineering (&ldquo;we&rdquo;, &ldquo;us&rdquo;, or &ldquo;our&rdquo;) respects your privacy.
            This Website Privacy Notice explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit
            <strong>KmTravels.com</strong> and related pages (the &ldquo;Website&rdquo;).
        </p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect information that you voluntarily provide when you:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Submit a contact or project inquiry form</li>
            <li>Subscribe to news or publications</li>
            <li>Communicate with us by email or phone</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We may also automatically collect certain technical information such as IP address, browser type, pages visited, and referring URLs through cookies and similar technologies, as described in our <a href="/cookies">Cookies Notice</a>.</p>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>To operate and maintain the Website</li>
            <li>To respond to inquiries and provide requested services</li>
            <li>To improve site performance and user experience</li>
            <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Sharing of Information</h2>
        <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with service providers who assist in operating the Website, subject to confidentiality obligations, or when required by law.</p>

        <h2>Your Choices</h2>
        <p>You may manage cookie preferences at any time using <button type="button" class="cookie-inline-link" onclick="snlCookieConsent.notifyOpenSettings()">Cookie Settings</button> in the site footer.</p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>For privacy-related questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@KmTravels.com">info@KmTravels.com</a> or visit our <a href="/contact">Contact</a> page.</p>
    </div>
</section>
